# Keel architecture context

This repository uses Keel for living software architecture. Before making structural changes, consult:

- `.keel/architecture/` — C4 diagrams
- `.keel/requirements/` — linked requirements
- `.keel/decisions/` — ADRs
- `.keel/characteristics/` — quality characteristics
- `.keel/specs/` — implementation work packages

When adding or moving code, update the relevant node `paths` globs in `.keel/architecture/*.json`.
